name: Naisu!
_comment-token: Your 'token' property is where you should put your bot token.
_comment-prefix: Your 'prefix' property is where you should put the prefix the bot will check for commands.
_comment-name: Your 'name' property is where you should put the name of your bot. This will appear at the bottom of many embeds.
_comment-embedcolor: Your 'embedcolor' property is where you should put the color you want to be used for most embed messages. This is in hexadecimal.
